  <description><![CDATA[<p><span>Centrally located right in the heart of Val Thorens, the Hotel Le Portillo offers comfortable and attractive accommodation as well as excellent skiing convenience. The superior hotel is uniquely decorated in a traditional mountain style and furnished with some beautiful antiques. Relax in the lounge or the sauna and hamman, the sun terrace is also great on bluebird days!</span></p>]]></description>
